Hindi pa ba sapat ang nakita mo?

00:31:48.030 --> 00:31:48.700
Master.

00:31:49.350 --> 00:31:50.460
Nasugatan din ako ni Zhulong.

00:31:50.480 --> 00:31:51.620
Bakit ayos lang ako?

00:31:52.000 --> 00:31:54.420
